{dx\over dt} = \sqrt{2g\sin\alpha \,x}\,.
{dx\over \sqrt{2g\sin\alpha x}} = dt\,,
\int_{x^\prime = 0}^x{dx^\prime\over\sqrt{2g\sin\alpha x^\prime}} = \int_{t^\prime = 0}^t{dt^\prime}\,.
